      <title>据称，业主 SBB 将于周二启动住宅单元 IPO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/landlord-sbb-is-said-to-kick-off-residential-unit-ipo-on-tuesday</link>
